entries.femaleVariant: Lemme guess, the bypass diodes disappeared again, too?
Got us runnin' in circles here. They klep the parts, we fix 'em, they klep the parts...
Fucking nomads. Typical. Think the whole world revolves around them. All theirs for the taking!
A solar farm?! More like an all-you-can-eat buffet! Be a real shame to let all these panels go to waste, huh?
Yeah... And no worries, some poor gonk out there'll fix it!
